# Supabase migrations

Schema / RLS changes for PetLink:

1. Add SQL under **`pbl-petlink-back-end/supabase/migrations/`**
2. Run **`npm run db:push`** from `pbl-petlink-back-end`

Do **not** use Supabase MCP `apply_migration` — it breaks migration history (`db push` / `db pull`).

See `pbl-petlink-back-end/.cursor/rules/supabase-migrations.mdc` for full workflow.
